@startuml
!theme plain
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
title Sequence — Generation d un Quiz (F2 + F3)

actor Etudiant
participant "React Frontend" as FRONT
participant "Django API\n/api/quiz/generate" as API
participant "RAG Service\nextract_text()" as RAG
participant "Ollama\n:11434" as OLLAMA
database "PostgreSQL" as DB

Etudiant -> FRONT : Upload PDF ou texte
FRONT -> FRONT : Validation client\n(taille <= 5Mo, texte >= 200c)
FRONT -> API : POST /api/quiz/generate\n{file | text, type}
API -> API : Verif JWT token\nVerif contraintes
API -> RAG : extract_text(source)
RAG -> RAG : PyPDF2 / text parse\nchunking + nettoyage
RAG -> OLLAMA : POST /api/generate\n{model: llama3.1:8b,\nprompt: system + doc}
OLLAMA --> RAG : stream JSON response\n10 questions QCM
RAG -> RAG : Parse JSON\nValidation Pydantic\n(schema strict)
RAG --> API : questions[] validees
API -> DB : INSERT Quiz\nINSERT 10 Questions
API --> FRONT : 201 Created\n{quiz_id, questions[]}
FRONT -> Etudiant : Affiche quiz interactif\n(10 QCM cliquables)

@enduml